The paper deals with image reconstruction using deep learning techniques, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The use of convolutional neural networks (CNNs) is also a key aspect of the paper, which falls under machine learning (cs.MM) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also involves training and evaluating the proposed network, which is a common theme in machine learning (cs.LG) and neural networks (cs.NE).
